Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.52,0:00:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Conan Edogawa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.02,0:00:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,High school student Shinichi was forced\Nto take a drug that shrunk him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.19,0:00:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although smaller, my mind remains\Nthat of a sharp detective!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.02,0:00:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's case takes place\Nin a haunted house!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's hidden in an eerie basement,\Nthere's always only one truth!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.74,0:00:21.19,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century in 100 years{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.83,0:00:27.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When told to cry, I laughed instead{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.03,0:00:39.50,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The first end of the century\Nin a long, long time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:45.59,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We're leaping into a wide open world{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:52.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The things I tried to\Nunderstand as a child{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.34,0:00:58.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}remain a mystery even as an adult{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:04.61,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm neither a hotshot\Nnor especially great{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.89,0:01:11.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I understand is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.19,0:01:16.92,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's neither an answer nor the truth{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:23.00,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I have faith in is\Nthe pounding of my heart{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:28.51,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That and nothing else {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.04,0:01:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Haunted House Murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come ghost hunting with us, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.13,0:02:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghost hunting?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.50,0:02:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about him, Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.01,0:02:40.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan wouldn't be any help\Neven if he did come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if it's just you and me who go...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where are these ghosts, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.52,0:02:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old mansion over on 4th Street!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,4th Street?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.52,0:02:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.06,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People call it a horror mansion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.86,0:02:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because a man was beaten\Nto death there 5 years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.78,0:03:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I do remember a mysterious\Nincident occurring there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.99,0:03:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say that after his wife\Nand son moved out,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,evil spirits took up\Nresidence in the house!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.88,0:03:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Evil spirits?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Late at night, people've heard\Nhorrible moaning coming from inside,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.30,0:03:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,stray dogs that wander inside\Nare found as skeletons the next day,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.80,0:03:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then last night, I saw a\Nspirit ball in one of the windows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Doesn't it make you excited?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing but nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In this scientific day and age,\Nghosts and monsters should be left
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to television and comic books.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.91,0:03:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are you calling Ayumi a liar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.66,0:03:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm just--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then come with us and prove\Nthat there aren't any ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.50,0:03:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you shouldn't\Nbe scared one bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.42,0:04:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Me, come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.42,0:04:05.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You believe me, don't you, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.68,0:04:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.22,0:04:12.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's get ourselves ready\Nand then beat up some ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:15.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they being serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all look at what we brought!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.71,0:04:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a metal ghost-hunting bat!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought snacks for when we're hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.67,0:04:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought flashlights for everyone\Nand a compass so we don't get lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Conan-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.55,0:04:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't really bring anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your own fault if you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You'll get killed\Nif you're careless!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.93,0:04:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try hard not to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.48,0:04:59.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do these guys think they're entering\Na devil's castle or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this gate won't open...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.69,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found a secret entrance\Nwhen I scouted out the place earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret entrance?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Here it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hidden by the grass,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.34,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it's just big enough\Nfor someone to go through! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing, Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.13,0:05:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A secret entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.10,0:05:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.06,0:05:35.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's open!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.44,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dark to see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.48,0:05:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It certainly is creepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.40,0:05:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... maybe we should go home...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.07,0:05:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See, it's even starting to rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.28,0:05:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be stupid! We didn't\Ncome this far for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.57,0:05:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can go home by yourself if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.83,0:06:01.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.84,0:06:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ayumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.76,0:06:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closer! It's just\Na sculpture of a demon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.23,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man! All I did was fall,\Nbut now my arms and legs are all dirty!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.44,0:06:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's been here for a long time,\Nso the floor's covered with dust...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.15,0:06:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a washroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.86,0:06:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.70,0:06:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walking around with you guys like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's almost like we're\Nin a role-playing game!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.83,0:06:42.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're in a party!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.04,0:06:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a brave fighter, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a cute girl warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.34,0:06:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a gifted magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.67,0:06:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'm a--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a villager!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.22,0:06:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But villagers aren't party members!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.01,0:06:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you're an important character--\Nyou give us information!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It's the perfect role for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bah! Don't patronize me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the deal, you guys? Hiding\Nbehind the villager, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.91,0:07:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get moving, villager!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.99,0:07:16.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun! You can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. The door opened\Nby itself because of the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:37.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what most "ghosts"\Nturn out to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:40.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost sound like a detective,\NMitsuhiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.81,0:07:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys wait here--\NI need to use the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.98,0:07:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you be alright by yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course! I have science\Nand logic on my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.32,0:07:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, this house sure is huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A really rich person\Nmust've lived here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ghosts can't possibly exist\Nin this scientific day and age!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was probably the sound of wind\Nblowing through a small hole
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.01,0:08:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.35,0:08:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! I'll check for myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.61,0:08:29.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These stairs go into the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.82,0:08:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those sounds are coming\Nfrom down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.82,0:08:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko-kun's taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:38.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been twenty minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.53,0:08:41.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he's going Number 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sound's getting louder...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Mitsuhiko's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.10,0:09:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.64,0:09:08.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There really {\i1}is {\i0}something\Nin this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:11.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mitsuhiko! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.73,0:09:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something! Mitsuhiko-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.03,0:09:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where could he have gone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.37,0:09:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't in the bathroom, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.78,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scream was no joke!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.66,0:09:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something must've\Nhappened to Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.00,0:09:27.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.00,0:09:30.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You two hide in a nearby room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.88,0:09:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to look for Mitsuhiko!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me! Don't leave\Nthe room, no matter what!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.43,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's not right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Supposedly no one's lived\Nhere ever since the murder,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so why isn't the water turned off?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.02,0:09:48.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's also that room\Nwith the open window!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The room hadn't been damaged\Nby wind or rain at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.07,0:09:55.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That means the window must've\Nbeen opened fairly recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.74,0:09:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's that secret entrance\Nthat was built out of plain view!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.91,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's been coming into\Nand leaving this mansion!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.91,0:10:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.62,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.09,0:10:14.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our moms must be worrying\Nabout us right about now...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.00,0:10:16.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already night outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.22,0:10:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan sure is taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.72,0:10:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These aren't for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.64,0:10:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuhiko-kun is probably\Nlost and hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun too...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.98,0:10:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are for them! You can't have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.85,0:10:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.40,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I smell food!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming from down there...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:42.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna check it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.83,0:10:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Conan-kun said not to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.50,0:10:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.04,0:10:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.63,0:10:56.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's strange! There're no signs\Nof anybody anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:10:58.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there's really nobody here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A photograph...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.97,0:11:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this the mansion's owner\Nwho was killed 5 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.31,0:11:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And is that his wife\Nand son behind him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that the killer\Nwas never caught,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.69,0:11:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that the remaining\Nfamily members moved away...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was Genta's voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit! I told him to hide!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.24,0:11:32.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun? What's the matter?\NDid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Genta-kun! Stop trying to scare me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.30,0:11:45.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Those aren't Genta-kun's footsteps!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then whose are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make any sounds!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.16,0:12:08.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.87,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.83,0:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, look closer! It's a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're just taking something somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.46,0:12:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.42,0:13:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.18,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.93,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any rooms around here,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.97,0:13:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and straight ahead is a dead-end!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.98,0:13:14.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So where did that person disappear to?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.64,0:13:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was a ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.15,0:13:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The dust on the floor has a line in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a second! Maybe this is a--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.20,0:13:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a door here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.16,0:13:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! That person just now\Nwent down through it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.33,0:13:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good! It's too much\Nfor a kid to open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.92,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call these Retractable Suspenders.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One push of a button and they retract\Nfrom their stretched-out state.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.30,0:13:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They should work great\Nfor tying up criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.47,0:13:53.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll try using these!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.18,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just watch and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A staircase to the basement!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:13.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe Mitsuhiko and Genta are down here!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see light!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A prison cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's it doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.73,0:14:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone in there!\NLook, on the bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is this guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:15.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another bad dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.81,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.77,0:15:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that was over 5 years ago--\Nforget about it already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.56,0:15:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you suffer,\Nit still won't bring him back to life...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back to life?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could she be referring to the\Nmurdered owner of this house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.53,0:15:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then these two people are--
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.99,0:15:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.34,0:15:55.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not keeping you locked up\Ndown here to make you suffer, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akio! I'm doing this so\Nthat you'll have a future!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.43,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha, now I see the truth behind\Nthis mansion and that murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.91,0:16:27.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like we have some more rats\Nthat snuck in with the other two...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show yourself.\NThere's no point in hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.84,0:16:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No point in hiding...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should\Ncome out of hiding, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.14,0:16:42.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found it in the study earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.23,0:16:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The photograph of you\Nand this house's owner,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.31,0:16:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who was murdered 5 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.02,0:16:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His appearance has drastically changed\Nin the 5 years he's lived down here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.86,0:16:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the man standing next to\Nyou in the picture is your son--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.41,0:16:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the man in that prison cell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.41,0:17:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The mole below his eye was the\Nonly thing that couldn't change.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.33,0:17:06.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought something was strange\Nwhen I first entered the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.58,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The family moved out so the\Nmansion should've been empty,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there was still running water.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.55,0:17:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, nobody is so frivolous\Nas to continually pay the water bill
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.68,0:17:21.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for a house that no one lives in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.60,0:17:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then there's that\Ndiscretely placed entrance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.69,0:17:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to the age\Nof the surrounding walls,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.77,0:17:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that wooden door was still new.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guess is that it was\Nbuilt after the incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...so that you could enter and leave\Nthe mansion without being seen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.41,0:17:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But as for why it was necessary\Nto make the place look uninhabited,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.91,0:17:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and why you needed to keep your son\Nlocked up in the basement...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those questions were answered\Nby your conversation just now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.05,0:17:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.88,0:17:57.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan Edogawa. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.05,0:17:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A detective?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.30,0:18:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are two possibilities\Nthat I can think of.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.93,0:18:07.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first is that the house's owner\Nwas killed by you, his wife,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:10.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that you locked your son up\Nbecause he witnessed the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:16.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second possibility is that it\Nwas your son who killed your husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.70,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing that he was the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you decided to protect your son\Nby hiding the truth behind the murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.66,0:18:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the weight of what he had\Ndone was too much for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:30.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The moans coming from this mansion\Nwere probably his deranged screams.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your son probably wanted to turn\Nhimself in to atone for his crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.13,0:18:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you couldn't allow that to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try to understand!\NThis is all for your sake!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.43,0:18:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You didn't want your son\Nto be known as a criminal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.02,0:18:53.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so you chose to keep him concealed\Nhere in absolute confinement.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.98,0:18:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from your conversation\Njust now and from your reaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.82,0:19:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your husband's killer must have been--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.53,0:19:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.33,0:19:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.37,0:19:13.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop, Mom! He's exactly right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.13,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I was\Nthe one who killed Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.01,0:19:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.43,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened on a spring night\N5 years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.56,0:19:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had just failed my\Nthird college entrance exam...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.81,0:19:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You failed another one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're an embarrassment to your family!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.28,0:19:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pathetic!\NYou're a waste of a person!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.36,0:19:41.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was already very mentally anguished,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.91,0:19:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so when I heard those words\Ncome from my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.37,0:19:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I lost control of myself\Nfor a split second!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Akio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:53.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I came to, I was holding a\Nblood-smeared candlestick in my hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:57.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my father was lying there\Non the floor, nearly unrecognizable!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.80,0:20:01.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you worry! I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.88,0:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.89,0:20:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest was just as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.81,0:20:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mom made it look\Nlike a robber killed him
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.39,0:20:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and then she stuck me in this cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't stand it any longer!\NI can't live like this anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.73,0:20:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,constantly haunted by\Nthe murder of my own father!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.07,0:20:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to confess my crime\Nso I can live with myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:24.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a hold of yourself, Akio!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.78,0:20:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there until the\Nstatute of limitations runs out!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep quiet, nobody will ever know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, if you remain in hiding like this,\Nyou will be able to escape the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:40.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll never escape from the guilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.38,0:20:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you intend to keep this\Nheavy weight on your son
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.22,0:20:46.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the rest of his life?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The night of terror came to an end,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and bright sunlight lit up the mansion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.62,0:21:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two who disappeared during the night
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.37,0:21:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,were found sleeping amiably\Nin the grass outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently the woman had put them\Nto sleep with an anesthetic
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and threw them out of the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.96,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That same day, the son and wife turned\Nthemselves in to the authorities,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.84,0:21:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a baffling murder case came\Nto an end after 5 long years.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, the four of us\Nwere scolded by the grownups...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure wish I was back in my normal body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:55.46,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just my imagination {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.58,0:22:05.22,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing with threads around my finger\Nwhile drinking lukewarm tea{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.93,0:22:14.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's walk lightly\Nto the bossa nova rhythm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.39,0:22:19.27,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The puzzle pieces are in my hands{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.48,0:22:25.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right... {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.69,0:22:35.41,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was in the same place last week\Nbut with different clothes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.75,0:22:42.84,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Step by step,\Nthere's no reason to be anxious{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.75,0:22:49.26,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Case by case,\NI don't care if you laugh{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.68,0:22:59.02,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Beyond the countless days,\Nshe's waiting for me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.44,0:23:03.57,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I gotta go my own way {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.87,0:23:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another haunted house?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.70,0:23:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Ayumi found another one!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.71,0:23:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This one's on 2nd Street,\Nand it belonged to the Eto family!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.42,0:23:21.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People living in the area say it's a\Nspooky mansion filled with weird books,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.96,0:23:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and a boy who used to live there\Nby himself was eaten by some monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boy who lived by himself in a\Nspooky mansion filled with books?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.56,0:23:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,2nd Street? Eto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.48,0:23:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, are you sure the name was Eto?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.48,0:23:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! You write it with a\Nkatakana "E" and a kanji "TO"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.19,0:23:51.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay! Let's get ready\Nto beat up some more ghosts!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.78,0:23:56.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's not "Eto"! That's "Kudo"!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my house!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, villager!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.83,0:24:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, villager!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.55,0:24:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.87,0:24:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to contact the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.49,0:24:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the knife\Nthey used during filming!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.05,0:24:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means the killer\Nwas someone on the staff!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.00,0:24:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.53,0:24:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I know the truth\Nbehind this incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.30,0:24:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan--
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.67,0:24:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The TV Drama Murder Case.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.23,0:24:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.63,0:24:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fu dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.30,0:24:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode is even more entertaining than a drama.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.59,0:24:56.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.03,0:24:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
